      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nSettled monetary transactions and purse-level closing balances from FIS STDMON + STDACCTBAL XTRACT. **Click any tile** to jump to member-level balances.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Settle Amount | `fact_monetary.settle_amount` | Dollar amount of settled transaction |\n| Txn Type Code | `fact_monetary.txn_type_code` | 1710=Value Load \u00b7 5=Purchase |\n| Closing Balance | `fact_account_balance.closing_balance` | Purse balance at end of reporting day |\n| Total Purchase | `fact_account_balance.total_purchase_amount` | Sum of all purchases that day |\n| Total Valueload | `fact_account_balance.total_valueload_amount` | Sum of all loads that day |\n\n> 166 members \u00b7 3 purses (FOD2100, OTC2100, CMB2100) \u00b7 $91,641 total closing balance.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
